data.lean: theorem add_right_cancel (a t b : mynat) : a + t = b + t → a = b :=
data.editorText:
intro h,
induction t with d hd,
repeat{rwa add_zero at h},
repeat{rw add_succ at h},

exact h2,

data.lean: lemma add_left_eq_zero {{a b : mynat}} (H : a + b = 0) : b = 0 :=
data.editorText:
cases b with c,
refl,
cases a with d,
rwa zero_add at H,
rw add_succ at H,
rw succ_add at H,
rw succ_eq_add_one (d + c) at H,
have h2 : succ (d + c + 1) ≠ 0 := succ_ne_zero (d + c + 1),
contradiction,
